{"tid":507014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國人做冬　兒冬至　中冬至　老冬至","createTime":"2017-12-22T19:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T07:40:46.000Z","uid":47714,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"918337dbd9f2a91042d7c410ba58fd5397f96928","tid":507014,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T19:09:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sjkorean/photos/a.173528062733808.46404.115930788493536/771671476252794/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsjkorean%2Fphotos%2Fa.173528062733808.46404.115930788493536%2F771671476252794%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=Rq0KpPxW9tA6I4%2Fq6ambdf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=c5cc58cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sjkorean/photos/a.173528062733808.46404.115930788493536/771671476252794/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n【韓國節慶】애동지 (兒冬至)<br />\n<br />\n冬至為一年四季中白晝最短、夜晚最漫長的一天。韓國習俗是在冬至時將紅豆煮得像粥一般濃稠，吃美味的팥죽(紅豆粥)，因為據說紅色可以擊退惡鬼；在紅豆粥中加入跟自己年紀一樣數量的湯圓，表示自己又增長了一歲。<br />\n<br />\n但是今年的冬至韓國不吃紅豆粥，而是改吃팥떡(紅豆年糕)。因為今年是&rdquo;애동지&rdquo; (兒冬至)的緣故。<br />\n<br />\n為什麼呢? 什麼是&quot;애동지&rdquo; (兒冬至)?<br />\n<br />\n冬至一般是每年國曆的12月22~23日，如果是落在農曆11月初~上旬期間，就稱為애동지(兒冬至)；若是在11月中旬就是중동지(中冬至)，而如果是在11月下旬的話，就是노동지(老冬至)。<br />\n<br />\n今年的冬至正好是農曆11月初1，所以是&rdquo;애동지&rdquo; (兒冬至)。<br />\n<br />\n韓國有一說，如果在애동지吃紅豆粥的話，對10歲以下的小孩子會有不好的事情發生。在韓國有位삼신할머니(三神娘娘)，類似於台灣的註生娘娘，逢產子或是為孩子祈福時便會祭拜三神娘娘。不過如果吃了紅豆粥驅鬼，就會連三神娘娘都一起趕走，那這樣三神娘娘就沒辦法保護小孩了。<br />\n<br />\n所以當애동지時，韓國家裡有小孩的家庭，為了小孩的關係而要改吃紅豆年糕，就是這個緣故。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://archive.is/0BQu7/6e1d5bccf5b7b3466c3166b7bf1650c02c8e70c0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.is%2F0BQu7%2F6e1d5bccf5b7b3466c3166b7bf1650c02c8e70c0&h=2bf2a1df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"520456a9459943f5a678f8778552b6229bacefa1","tid":507014,"uid":31887,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T19:10:59.000Z","msg":"狗都有年糕食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c4b8f8e3cd7615f42a2e933c626c6bc73617c5","tid":507014,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T19:21:18.000Z","msg":"啊啊啊啊啊啊～金正日冬至<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uEullB7zeJk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuEullB7zeJk&d=Rq0KpPxW9tA6I4%2Fq6ambdf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4edae9a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uEullB7zeJk</a>"},{"pid":"e84246e3e5f635aefbf613daa917413a8182c09d","tid":507014,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T07:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8c7c327ea63cd4ad663a97542fa21dadb9fba1","tid":507014,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T07:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}